FDP Says Greek Deal May Defy Bundestag, Tagesspiegel Reports

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-07-21T16:47:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/fdp-says-greek-deal-may-defy-bundestag-tagesspiegel-reports.html
German Free Democratic Party
lawmaker  Frank Schaeffler  said a euro-area agreement on  Greece 
that involves buying the country’s bonds may contravene a
resolution passed in February by the German parliament, or
Bundestag,  Tagesspiegel  reported.  Schaeffler in an interview published today said that the
Bundestag should convene a special session to debate the outcome
of the euro-area leaders’ summit in Brussels, the newspaper
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
 jblack25@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  